    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 9. Head, costal area of hemelytron and antenna in males of Catoplatus spp. 1 – 3. head: 1 — C. immarginatus; 2 — C. fulvicornis; 3 — C. guentheri. 4 – 7. costal area: 4 — C. guentheri; 5 — C. fulvicornis; 6 — C. immarginatus; 7 — C. citrinus; 8, 9. antenna: 8 — C. guentheri; 9 — C. fulvicornis. Scale bar 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/214443/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

